</P>
<P>
JERUSALEM -- Israeli troops are embracing for riots and
violence in the West Bank and Gaza Strip in the coming weeks
surrounding a Palestinian declaration of statehood, an Israeli
newspaper said on Monday.
</P>
<P>
The English-language daily Ha'aretz said IDF (Israeli Defense
Forces) is preparing vehicles, helicopters and tanks to confront
possible violent clashes with Palestinians in another popular
uprising, or Intifada. (Israel-Palestinian)
