in harmony with resolutions taken by the Organization of Petroleum
Exporting Countries (OPEC) to stabilize world oil market.
</P>
<P>
Obaid bin Saif Al Naseri, the minister of Petroleum and Mineral
Resources, said any step in that direction should be made within
the OPEC collective framework, the Emirates News Agency (WAM)
reported.
</P>
