about an agreement on the permanent status of the Palestinian
territories in a fixed period of time as has been stated in an
agreement reached in September 1999 between Israel and
Palestinians.
</P>
<P>
"Such an agreement will help create the conditions for the
emergence of a sovereign and democratic (Palestinian) state which
is livable in an atmosphere of cooperation with Israel," said the
spokeswoman.
</P>
<P>
Israeli Prime Minister Ehud Barak will arrive here Thursday to
have talks with French President Jacques Chirac at a time when the
Middle East peace process is faced with serious setbacks.
</P>
<P>
Barak is expected to call on France to help stop the
Palestinian plan to declare unilaterally an independent state.
</P>
<P>
