<TEXT>

<P>
PHNOM PENH, July 4 (Xinhua) -- The two-day congress of the
ruling Cambodian People's Party (CPP) ended here Tuesday with a
conclusion to endorse closer cooperation with its coalition
partner, the royalist FUNCIPEC party, as well as with all
political parties and patriotic forces to jointly consolidate
peace, stability and national development.
</P>
