<HEADLINE> News Items From Asia-Pacific Desk of Xinhua (Part 1) </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
HONG KONG, July 4 (Xinhua) -- Following are news items from the
Asia-Pacific Desk of Xinhua in Hong Kong Tuesday:
</P>
<P>
Major News Items in Leading Philippine Newspapers
</P>
<P>
Hopes Dim for Indonesian Ship Passengers to Survive
