<HEADLINE> Taiwan's Issuance of New Banknote Brings No Change to Its Status as Part of China: Spokesman </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
BEIJING, July 4 (Xinhua) -- A spokesman of the Taiwan Affairs
Office of the State Council said here today that the issuance of
the new version of the banknotes in Taiwan will bring about no
change to its status as part of China's territory.
</P>
