<HEADLINE> Ukrainian Parliament Leader Hopes to Strengthen Ties with Poland </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
KIEV, July 3 (Xinhua)-- Ukrainian parliament hopes to maintain
a good-neighborly relationship with Poland, said parliament
Chairman Ivan Pliusch Monday when meeting with a visiting
parliament delegation.
</P>
<P>
Pliusch told Sejm Speaker Maciej Plazynski, head of the Polish
delegation, that his country regards Poland as its strategic
partner and that the two nations' stands on strategic issues "
coincide."
</P>
